### 环境变量
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@captainToken = YOUR_CAPTAIN_TOKEN_HERE

###############################################
# 二、商品分类模块 (Category)
###############################################

### 2.1 获取分类列表（团长端）
GET {{baseUrl}}/captain/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{captainToken}}

### 2.2 创建分类
POST {{baseUrl}}/captain/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{captainToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试分类",
  "sort": 100
}

### 2.3 更新分类
# 将 :id 替换为实际的分类 ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/captain/categories/6
Authorization: Bearer {{captainToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后的分类名称",
  "sort": 101
}

### 2.4 删除分类
# 将 :id 替换为实际的分类 ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/captain/categories/6
Authorization: Bearer {{captainToken}}

###############################################
# 居民端
###############################################

### 2.5 获取分类列表（居民端）
@residentToken = YOUR_RESIDENT_TOKEN_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/resident/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{residentToken}}
